	<div id="content"><section class="my-16 c-centered-icon-title-text tablet:my-24 js-in-viewport">
    <div class="o-wrapper o-wrapper--narrow">
                    <img src="/wp-content/themes/bulmer-leisure/img/icon-silver.svg" alt="Bulmer Leisure Icon" class="mx-auto mb-5">
                            <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-heading text-black text-center mb-5">Silver Bay Holiday Park in Rhoscolyn, Anglesey</h1>
                            <div class="u-editor-content">
                <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you have ever dreamt of owning a holiday home in Anglesey by the sea, then there is nowhere better than Silver Bay Holiday Park in Rhoscolyn.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">We’re proud to offer a beautiful and unique family holiday park on the North Wales Coast, with multi million pound award winning facilities and breath taking Anglesey scenery. You will find an exceptional collection of luxury holiday lodges and static caravans for sale at our seaside resort &#8211; perfect if you are looking for your very own place to escape to in the UK. </span></p>
            </div>
                    </div>
</section>

    <div class="c-masonry-grid my-16 tablet:my-24 js-in-viewport">
        <div class="o-wrapper">
            <div class="c-masonry-grid__container grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr]">
                <div class="h-full w-full grid grid-rows-[2fr_1fr] gap-5">
                    <div class="h-full w-full grid grid-cols-2 gap-5">

                        <div class="h-full w-full grid grid-rows-2 gap-5">

