                                    <div class="mb-0 c-feature-banner__text-column u-editor-content">
                        <p>You can choose to take full ownership of our lodges or caravans or opt for fractional shared ownership of one of our luxury lodges. With fractional ownership, you will split the time spent in your lodge over the course of the year with other aspiring Anglesey holiday homeowners. This is a more affordable option than outright ownership, perfect for anyone who is keen to enjoy the many benefits of holiday home ownership at a reduced rate. Whichever option you choose, you will still have access to our wide selection of on‐site facilities throughout the year.</p>
<p>Our Fractional Shared Ownership model allows you to experience the many benefits of luxury lodge ownership without the year-long commitment and at a fraction of the cost.</p>
                    </div>
                                                    <div class="mb-0 u-editor-content">
